&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Acting as the main point of contact for customers to execute large trades with them e.g. making and receiving OTC quotes to customers as well as sourcing counter-trades.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensuring that any anticipated OTC trades are pre-funded or have adequate credit facilities available.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining strong relationships with traders and institutional customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing any OTC trade disputes and OTC Working Capital.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the Analysts and back office are providing timely settlement through well-established and tech-enabled processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
